Nanine Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanine_Wright 0 Nanine Wright (June 3, 1876 – May 23, 1947) was an American silent film actress. She is known for her roles in Risky Business (1920) and the lost film serial Graft as Mrs. Larnigan. Nanine_Wright ( June_3_,_1876 – May_23_,_1947 ) was an_American_silent_film_actress .
